claim.claim-text:
1. A molding information printing system, comprising:
a network;
a molding machine connected to said network;
a printer for printing molding information of said molding machine;
a print control section connected to said network independently of said molding machine, for controlling said printer for printing of said molding information; and
an instructing section for instructing printing of said molding information and transferring a command to said print control section through said network.
